"3 tablespoons minced shallots","2 tablespoons white wine vinegar","1 tablespoon grated orange rind","1/4 cup fresh orange juice","2 teaspoons minced fresh or 1/2 teaspoon dried thyme","1/2 teaspoon salt","2 teaspoons extra-virgin olive oil","3 cups small mushrooms (about 8 ounces)","  Freshly ground black pepper (optional)"